```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
 [1] -0.24457065  0.73378542  2.85278145  0.67152530 -0.11584926 -1.30135199
 [7] -0.91780026  0.05071605 -0.38013286  0.72262510
```


:::
:::

